guangdong exports 3.76 billion us dollars of new high level technology products
xinhua news agency , guangzhou , march 16 ( reporter chen ji ) the latest statistics show that from january to february of this year , exports of new high level technology products in guangdong province were 3.76 billion us dollars , an increase of 34.8% compared with the same period last year , accounting for 25.5% of the province 's total export value .
high - tech products have been exported frequently , making important contributions to the growth of guangdong 's foreign trade .
last year , the province 's exports of high @- and new - technology products were 229.4 billion us dollars , up 31 percent from the same period of last year , up 27.2 percentage points from the province 's growth rate of exports , while the net increase of exports of new @- and high - tech products was 5.27 billion us dollars , making up for the decrease in traditional labor - intensive exports due to price declines .
among the new high level technology products exported by guangdong , computer and communication technologies alone outperformed others . last year , exports were 19.14 billion us dollars , accounting for 85.9 percent of the province 's total export value of new high level technology products .
the main markets for the export of guangdong 's high - tech products are hong kong , the united states , the european union and japan .
last year , the total value of exports of the new and high - tech industrial belts in the pearl river delta reached 22.99 billion us dollars , accounting for 98.7% of the total export volume of new and high - tech products of the whole province .
this year , the leading role is still very prominent .
currently , computers in the pearl river delta region have a complete set rate of over 95 percent , and are capable of providing all computer parts except the pnets .
fifa to severely punish deception on soccer pitch
xinhua news agency , brussels , march 17 , the world cup finals will be more rigorous in dealing with players who make profits by means of fake fall , according to the fifa executive board on tuesday .
the fifa executive board said in a press release that they would fully support the strict enforcement of the judgment , especially against the players who cheat viewers .
the fifa executive committee also announced some reform measures .
the fifa rules that starting from july 1 this year , fifa will not be allowed to write any words on the player 's vest , while fifa allows the player to take off the ball for celebration , but they must be in front of the sport uniform .
suicide bombing in jerusalem
xinhua news agency report of march 17 from jerusalem ( by staff reporter zhong cuihua and nie xiaoyang ) - a man blew up a bomb carrying him on a bus in a residential area in northern jerusalem on the afternoon of the 17 th . the person himself was killed on the spot , and nine others were slightly injured and sent to hospital for treatment .
the police have already sealed off the scene of the explosion .
less than two hours ago , a palestinian shooting incident took place in the town of kapara in northern israel .
according to the latest report , a 16 - year - old israeli girl was killed , and at least 12 others were injured .
the gunmen shot dead .
at present , no group has claimed responsibility for the attack .
the israeli prime minister 's office condemned the shooting .
israeli prime minister sharon said on the same day that although israel and the palestinian side are making cease - fire efforts , the israeli side will respond to any attack .
public invited to participate in painting and calligraphy competition
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , march 18 this year marks the fifth anniversary of hong kong 's return to the motherland and also marks the promulgation and implementation of china 's first " code of conduct for public servants . " in order to celebrate these two happy events , a painting and calligraphy competition with the theme of " state civil servants - public servants - the people 's public servants " will be carried out among civil servants in hong kong , macao , and the mainland .
the competition was sponsored by hong kong wen wei po , the china mayors ' association , and the hong kong cultural and leisure affairs department .
civil servants participating in the competition will create chinese paintings to demonstrate the scenery of the motherland 's various places and write poetry , and will also use the code of conduct jointly observed by civil servants as the content of calligraphy work , such as well - known well - known well - known sayings , sayings , and police lines to encourage civil servants to honestly perform their official duties , diligently perform their official duties , and faithfully fulfill their duties , thereby raising the cultural accomplishments and professional standards of civil servants .
the competition will highlight the festive atmosphere of the fifth anniversary of hong kong 's return to china and fully demonstrate the artistic charm of chinese paintings and calligraphy .
it has been learned that the collection of works for this painting and calligraphy competition will be completed on 20 april 2002 .
the winning entries will be released on the 5 th anniversary of the reunification of hong kong .
anc opposes sanctions against zimbabwe
xinhua news agency , johannesburg , march 18 ( reporter : liu plateau ) on the 18th , secretary general of the african national congress ( anc ) of south africa , motort , criticized western countries here , such as the united states and britain , in an attempt to force zimbabwe to act in accordance with the wishes of western countries by imposing sanctions .
in response to western countries ' threat of imposing sanctions on zimbabwe , motort told the press : " as for who should zimbabwe lead , the zimbabwean people 's own affairs cannot be decided by western countries . "
he pointed out that mutual respect for national sovereignty is an international norm that every country must abide by , and the anc is firmly opposed to the sanctions imposed on a sovereign country by western countries .
if western countries impose further sanctions on zimbabwe , not only will it be of no help , it will also aggravate social unrest in zimbabwe , the minister said .
he called on the zimbabwean government and opposition parties to work together to overcome difficulties such as food shortage and land crisis .
he stressed that only by strengthening unity will it be possible to defeat any attempt to split zimbabwe .
earlier , the anc issued a statement demanding that the international community respect the choice of the zimbabwean people and help them tide over the difficulties .
zimbabwean president robert mugabe was re - elected president from march 9 to 11 , but western countries accused the election of having serious pitfalls and lack of fairness and freedom , and refused to recognize the election results and threatened to impose further sanctions on zimbabwe .
at present , some western countries have already announced the termination of economic aid to zimbabwe .
prior to the election , eu countries imposed " targeted " sanctions against zimbabwe on the grounds that zimbabwean government restricted press freedom and obstructed supervision .
french athletes returned to paris to participate in the winter olympics
xinhua news agency , paris , march 18 ( reporter wang jingcheng ) french athletes who took part in the winter games for the disabled held in salt lake city , the united states , from march 7 to 16 returned to paris today .
at the charles de gaulle airport , the athletes were warmly welcomed by the french minister of youth sports , beatrix , who is in charge of the work of families , children , and disabled people .
the french delegation participating in the eighth olympiad for the handicapped held in salt lake city , the united states won a total of 19 medals . female athletes won nine medals , including one gold medal , and male athletes won 10 medals , including one gold medal .
this was the best result of the french delegation at the winter olympics .
at the welcoming ceremony , cellucci said that french athletes have changed society 's views on them with their special performance . the french people are grateful for their outstanding contributions to changing people 's views on the disabled .
the minister said in his speech that the french government will , as always , continue to support disabled sports .
