at present , the emphasis of his training is on defense and he also practices drawing basketball .
he planned to increase the strength of his body slightly to check if he could fit .
he said that his knees were at least 100 percent better than before the operation . "
jordan scored an average score of 243.30 for this season . he underwent an operation three weeks ago . the team won four wins and eight losses during this period .
at present , there are only 15 regular matches with the chiangs - 31 team taking 36 seats , ranking 10 th in the eastern alliance , behind miami heat wave to lead the fierce dragon team one time , but they still have two and a half matches compared with the eighth place in charlotte hornets .
the coach of qazi naturally hoped that jordan 's comeback would bring about a leap forward in the quality of the team and at least be able to win continuously in a short period of time , thus setting off the hope of the post - season games again .
