south korea to send message to north korea on resumption of talks
xinhua news agency , seoul , march 19 ( reporter zhang li ) according to a report by south korea 's yonhap news agency , the south korean government has made a request to indonesian president megawati , hoping that she will convey to north korean leader kim dae - jung the message that south korean president kim dae - jung hopes to resume south - north korean talks and north - us talks as soon as possible .
a south korean government official said that information content includes that both south korea and the united states hope to resolve the problem with north korea through dialogue and hope that north korea will adopt a positive attitude .
