israeli prime minister sharon summoned the core minister for consultations on the current israeli - palestinian situation and how to deal with the increasingly frequent explosion attacks on the palestinian side that afternoon . the meeting decided to step up military strikes against the palestinian side .
a person in political circles here disclosed that the security cabinet holds that intensifying attacks on palestine will weaken the momentum of terrorist activities in pakistan , but it is impossible to stop such attacks at all .
sharon will deliver a televised speech to the whole country at 8 : 30 p.m . local time on the evening of 31 april ( 1130 gmt ) to explain to the public the government 's stand on handling the israeli - palestinian conflict .
cambodia - vietnam trade fair opens
xinhua news agency , phnom penh , april 1 ( reporter yan ming ) an exhibition of nearly 200 commodities opened here today .
fifty firms from cambodia and vietnam participated in the exhibition , setting up 55 exhibition booths .
the exhibits include motorcycles , home appliances , agricultural tools , medicines , beverages , food and clothing .
speaking at the opening ceremony , vietnamese ambassador to cambodia nguyen dai hong said that vietnam and cambodia have great potential in developing economic and trade relations , and the holding of the commodities fair will further promote economic and trade cooperation and exchanges between the two countries .
he said : in recent years , the volume of trade between the two countries has made gratifying progress , increasing from $11.9 billion in 2000 to $11.8 billion in 2001 .
ceba said : the joint development of trade and economic cooperation between cambodia and vietnam is a good thing . it is conducive to promoting economic and trade relations between the two countries and also to promoting economic development in the asean countries . it will enable cambodia and vietnam to merge with the economies of asean and the world at an early date .
