it was predicted that there will be sandstorms in central and southern inner mongolia , the northern part of shaanxi , shanxi , and hebei , and in some areas of liaoning and jilin provinces and there will be strong sandstorms , in some areas there will be floating dust or sand , with temperatures falling by 6 to 12 degrees celsius , and temperatures in some areas exceeding 14 degrees celsius .
