candidates taking part in the presidential election include natanh gusmao and sha villear .
gusmao was the leader of the east timor independent movement , which was founded in november 1975 as the president of the democratic republic of east timor .
the two candidates held a public debate in imperial power on the 11 th and answered questions raised by voters .
gusmao said he would first work to solve the country 's economic problems after winning the election and that the government would ensure democracy in the country .
public opinion generally believes that gusmao is very likely to win because he is considered an independent hero in east timor .
east timor held a national referendum on august 30 , 1999 , under the direction of the united nations , and the overwhelming majority of voters cast their votes for independence .
on august 30 last year , east timor officially elected a constitution - making council and adopted its first constitution in march this year .
the new constitution will take effect on 20 may when east timor is officially independent , and the constitution of the country will become the first national assembly .
