the army that supports chavez then issued an ultimatum to the coup military to release chavez and occupied the tiwu barracks , a key strategic location .
in the early morning of 14 april , chavez returned to the presidential palace by helicopter from a small caribbean island .
xinhua news agency , damascus , april 15 ( reporter gong zhenxi ) bastiz al - assad , president of syria , held talks with visiting us secretary of state colin powell here on the 15th . the two sides discussed the latest developments in the middle east situation , especially the serious situation in palestine and tensions in the lebanon - israel border area .
according to the syrian news agency , president bashar al - asad said in his talks : " the palestinian incident has caused the ( middle east ) peace process to enter a dead - end . if we cannot understand this , the development of the matter may be irrecoverable . by that time , we can only wait for another generation of people . "
he pointed out that the peace process could only be discussed after israel withdrew its troops from the palestinian territories it occupied and stopped killing palestinians .
he said : " only when both sides wish to realize peace can peace be realized . "
he called on the united states to have a clear view on peace in the middle east and play a role in this regard so that relevant un resolutions can be truly implemented .
bashar said that these actions were not the root cause of the current events in the occupied palestinian territories , but the consequence of which was a counterattack against israel 's acts .
he pointed out that the best way is to eliminate the root cause of tensions in palestine .
according to diplomatic sources , during the talks , powell and bashar also discussed the issue of the lebanon - israel border situation .
powell arrived in damascus at noon on the same day for a short visit to syria .
new york stocks fall
xinhua news agency , new york , april 15 , the dow jones index fell to its lowest level in eight weeks due to poor performance of citigroup and continental airlines .
the dow jones industrial average closed down 97.15 at 10,893.67 , the lowest since february 22 . the technology heavy nasdaq composite index fell 2.41 at 1,753.78 . standard ; poor 's 500 index fell 8.46 to 1,102.55 .
the nyse composite index and the russell 2000 index of smaller companies also fell 0.74 at 436.05 .
advancing issues outnumbered decliners by a 5 - to - 4 margin on the new york stock exchange , with nyse volume down to 11.2 billion shares from 12.6 billion in the previous session .
on the same day , citibank announced that due to its loss in operations in argentina , the bank failed to achieve its expected profit for the first quarter of this year , and continental airlines also declared that it was losing money in the first quarter of this year .
investors were worried about the performance of the listed companies that will be announced this week , thus maintaining a wait - and - see attitude .
wall street stocks fell after a slight fall , and trading volume remained low for the whole day .
blue chip stocks such as citibank , mainland china airlines , and general electric , and science and technology such as microsoft , intel , cke , oracle , dell , and solar microelectronics all fell .
