xinhua news agency , jerusalem , april 16 ( reporter zhong cuihua ) visiting us secretary of state colin powell will hold talks with israeli prime minister ariel sharon and palestinian national authority chairman yasser arafat on the afternoon of the 16th and the morning of the 17th respectively .
it has been reported that powell has delayed for at least 24 hours his departure from the middle east region , and israel will continue to mediate between israel and palestine .
powell expressed the hope that israel and palestine will issue a joint statement condemning the terrorist attacks on israelis and palestinians , and calling for the establishment of a palestinian state through negotiations and continued efforts to crack down on terrorism .
powell concluded his one - day visit to lebanon and syria on the evening of 15 november and returned to israel , and announced at midnight that he would cancel the original plan to hold talks with arafat on 16 february .
powell told the press that the united states supports sharon 's proposal on holding a regional meeting and said that arafat may send a high - level delegation to the meeting .
in response to this , ' arafat has said that the palestinians can accept the proposal of holding a regional peace meeting only if israel immediately withdraws from the palestinian - controlled areas in the west bank .
powell held talks with sharon on 12 july .
on 14 july , he went to ramallah , the west bank city of the jordan river , where he held talks with arafat , who was surrounded by the israeli army .
in the evening , he briefed sharon on his talks with arafat .
