xinhua news agency , kabul , april 16 ( reporter shang xuqian ) visiting united nations high commissioner for refugees ( unhcr ) lambles met with hamid karzai , chairman of the interim government , on the evening of the 15 th . the two sides held talks on the return of albanian refugees and their re - integration into society .
the united nations high commissioner for refugees ( unhcr ) said in a press release today that he stressed the importance of re - integration of refugees into society to achieve stability in afghanistan .
he stressed that the safety of refugees in rural areas must be ensured and that the safety of refugees in rural areas is of great importance to preventing too many refugees from flowing into the cities .
karzai thanked the unhcr for its long - term efforts in afghanistan .
he said the re - integration of refugees into society was one of the priorities of the interim government .
he stressed that the return of the homeless in the country to their native place is an urgent issue to be resolved .
he said that the situation in most regions of afghanistan was stable , with adequate rainfall , and these people could immediately resume farming after returning to their native land and achieve self - sufficiency in food supply .
according to hassan , spokesman of the united nations high commissioner for refugees ( unhcr ) , more than 240,000 afghan have returned to their homeland from pakistan since the unhcr and the afghan interim government officially started the campaign to help the refugees return home on march 1 .
forty percent of these people went to the cities .
sears arrived in afghanistan after concluding his visit to iran .
he will leave for pakistan on the 17 th .
