putin 's state of the union address
xinhua news agency , moscow , april 18 , russian president putin said in his state of the union address at the joint session of the russian parliament on the 18th that russia should become a economically powerful and competitive country and should strive to develop constructive normal relations with all countries in the world and become a true member of the international community .
putin said : russia 's national construction goals are still to develop democracy and build a civilized market economy , and the most important thing is to improve the people 's living standards .
summing up last year 's work , he pointed out that the country has achieved certain results in fulfilling its major tasks , the economy has maintained sustained growth , the number of unemployed people has decreased , the people 's livelihood has improved to some extent , and russians are full of confidence in the future .
putin expressed satisfaction with the good implementation of the budget for two consecutive years and the improvement of the operating environment .
he stressed in particular that russia ranks second in the world in petroleum output and ranks first in the world in energy trade .
in his state of the nation address , putin also expounded on the state development plan and domestic and foreign policies for this year .
this is putin 's third state of the nation address to both the house and the senate since he assumed office as president .
more than 600 congressmen , 89 principal leaders of the federation , responsible persons of the presidential office and government departments , and nearly 1,000 people attended the joint meeting .
fm spokesman on european parliament report
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 19 , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue commented on a report passed by the european parliament ( ep ) here today .
a reporter asked : on 11 april , the plenary session of the european parliament deliberated and adopted the " report of the european parliament on the eu commission 's strategic document on china . "
what is china 's comment on this ?
zhang qiyue answered : china has taken note of the recent adoption of this report by the european parliament .
the report holds that there are broad common interests between china and the eu , advocating the development of sino - eu partnership , strengthening bilateral contacts , exchanges , and dialogue , and expanding bilateral cooperation in the economic and trade , scientific and technological , educational , and cultural fields .
we welcome the above - mentioned positive proposals .
however , the report made many erroneous conclusions that are inconsistent with objective facts on china 's human rights situation and on the taiwan and tibet issues , and seriously interfered in china 's internal affairs . this is unacceptable to the chinese side .
it is hoped that the european parliament will earnestly abide by the one - china principle and do more things beneficial to the development of bilateral relations so as to avoid creating a negative impact on sino - european relations .
