various kinds of enterprises in hebei province actively apply for foreign trade rights
xinhua news agency , shijiazhuang , april 20 ( reporter rao yajie ) the reporter learned from the hebei provincial foreign trade and economic cooperation department that since the beginning of this year , nearly 200,000 enterprises of various types have registered their foreign trade management rights at the provincial foreign trade and economic cooperation department , or have been approved by the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation , which is 2.3 times that of the same period last year .
so far , 39 foreign trade companies have registered , of which 17 are private foreign trade companies .
there are also dozens of commercial , material , and supply and marketing cooperatives enterprises and state - owned collective enterprises .
77 private production enterprises have also reported their foreign trade rights .
the entry of more and more private enterprises into the wto is a new atmosphere now applying for foreign trade rights .
in july last year , the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation further relaxed the conditions and standards for all types of enterprises to operate their import and export operations . the original examination and approval procedures were changed to a system of examining and approving the import and export business and a system of registration . the regulations stipulate unified standards and management methods for enterprises under various ownership systems , and this promoted the initiative of enterprises of all types to submit applications .
israel to cooperate with un investigation team
xinhua news agency , jerusalem , april 20 ( reporters zhong cuixiang , xu shanyue ) israeli government officials said on the 20th that israel would send un committees for the investigation of the truth at jenin refugee camp in the west bank of jordan river to cooperate .
israeli radio quoted israeli government officials as saying that the israeli side will show the un delegation video tapes on the israeli troops carrying out military actions in the jenin refugee camp and allow the delegation members to cover the soldiers and commanders involved in the military action , hoping that the delegation will remain objective and fair in the course of investigation .
the security council of the united nations today unanimously passed a resolution on the united states to welcome the investigation of the refugee camp at jenin .
just a few hours before the vote , israeli foreign minister shimon peres made a phone call to un secretary general annan , saying that israel would welcome " clarification " of the truth of the refugee camp in jenin .
on the same day , annan also talked with israeli defense minister bin aleazer over the phone , and bin aleazer also expressed his agreement with the un delegation to conduct an investigation .
it is reported that both bin aleazer and peres claimed that the israeli troops exchanged fire with palestinian militants during their military operations in the jenin refugee camp , killing 23 israeli soldiers and killing 50 palestinian people , most of whom were palestinian militants .
recently , there have been loud cries from the international community for investigation of the jenin refugee camp conflict , which has recently been the most violent conflict between israel and palestine .
the palestinian side accused the israeli army of slaughtering the palestinian people there , causing hundreds of deaths , but israel flatly denied this .
china dissatisfied with koizumi 's visit to yasukuni shrine
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 21 , chinese foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue pointed out here today that the chinese side firmly opposes japanese leaders visiting the yasukuni shrine in any form and at any time , which houses the memorial tablets of class - a war criminals .
the chinese side expresses strong dissatisfaction at the action taken by the japanese leader .
in response to a question on japanese prime minister junichiro koizumi 's visit to the yasukuni shrine this morning , zhang qiyue said : japan 's action can only damage its own image and make it more difficult for japan to win the trust of the people of asian countries on the historical issue .
this is junichiro koizumi 's second visit to the yasukuni shrine since he took office .
the yasukuni shrine is the place for japan to pay respects to servicemen who died in wars ( mostly wars of aggression ) since the meiji restoration , and class a war criminals such as hideki tojo in world war ii are enshrined there .
first round of voting for french presidential election
xinhua news agency , paris , april 21 ( reporter liang guihe ) the first round of voting for french presidential election began at 8 : 00 a.m . on the 21st in france 's 640,000 polling stations .
of the 16 candidates , 40 million voters will elect the seventh president of the republic of france .
the result of the poll was announced on the evening of the same day .
french voters ' turnout was 21.41 percent at noon on november 21 , down from 22.52 percent in the first round of voting in 1995 , the interior ministry said in a press release .
the media predict that this year 's turnout rate may be the lowest in history .
the french constitution stipulates that if no candidate gets more than 51 percent of the votes in the first round of voting , then the two candidates with the highest votes will enter the second round of voting on may 5 .
the results of last friday 's public opinion poll showed that incumbent president chirac and incumbent prime minister jospin may win very close votes in the first round .
since there are as many as 16 candidates in the presidential election , which is the highest record in french history , voters may be scattered in the first round of voting .
lein , presidential candidate of the french far - right national front , may rank third in the first round , and may even emerge as the first two " cold faces " .
