( comprehensive report from washington ) according to a report in the latest issue of the new york times , iraqi intelligence agencies have all along maintained close ties with the qazi , who is the mastermind of the 9 / 11 attacks .
it is reported that these two organizations will jointly command a terrorist organization in the kurdistan area in northern iraq .
