these officials praised the report carried by the new york weekly the day before yesterday , saying that the report was the latest basis for their support of their arguments .
it is reported that there is an ansa muslim guerrilla force in iraq 's kurdistan district composed of kurdistan and arab people who had received training at the camp in aoma .
