us senator : flu - infected terrorists can spread at airport
( united states , washington , d . c . ) us senator frist warned at a hearing on biological and chemical weapons the day before yesterday that terrorists infected with the sky would spread the deadly virus or infection at the airport , which could cause the virus to spread throughout the country and could lead to tens of thousands or even millions of deaths .
frist said at the hearing that the infected terrorists entered an airport . he could pass the virus to 10 innocent passengers through cough , sneezing , or breathing alone . these 10 passengers may then spread the virus to the whole country and may even kill tens of thousands or even millions of people .
he said that this may be a possible form of weapons of mass destruction .
it does not need to be launched with missiles , nor does it need to attract people 's attention like anthrax .
those infected victims and those who prevent such attacks may never know where these viruses ( germs ) come from .
experts told the senate foreign relations committee : this is part of the reason why biochemical weapons are in danger .
biden , chairman of the senate foreign relations committee , said that preventing attacks by biochemical weapons is an extremely urgent issue that must be resolved .
jesse helms , a republican member with the highest qualifications in the committee , said that the united states still needs to build a missile defense system in order to prevent the enemy from carrying any kind of warhead to attack the united states .
several hundred thousand u.s. and south korean soldiers conduct large - scale exercise
( seoul , new york ) several hundred thousand us and south korean soldiers will conduct a military exercise of the largest scale simulating the korean conflict on thursday , drawing pyongyang 's attack on it as a provocative act of war .
on the eve of a week - long military exercise , us military officers said that the exercise was purely defensive in nature , but it occurred after the seoul authorities warned that the korean issue should not be ignored .
this was the largest military exercise since the 1950 - 53 korean war , and because it did not conclude a formal treaty on ending the conflict on the korean peninsula , it became the last front of the cold war in the world , with nearly two million troops living on the border .
the us - rok coalition command in seoul said that the exercise from 21 to 27 march will be the first time to test its effectiveness by combining two different joint military exercises .
this means that hundreds of thousands of soldiers will join , but the military has not disclosed details .
a spokesman for the coalition command said that almost every us military unit and south korean military unit on the korean peninsula and us troops from outside will be mobilized this exercise .
30,000 us troops frequently stationed in south korea to prevent north korea from launching an attack by 1.1 million troops .
south korea also has 650,000 troops .
the joint command claimed that this exercise was a combination of the computerized military exercise and the annual " little eagle " exercise .
in the past few years , the company mobilized 500,000 south korean troops and 30,000 us troops ( including 20,000 us troops from outside ) in the exercise alone .
north korea accused the united states of staging a joint military exercise in an attempt to provoke a war .
the official " labor news " even claimed that the us - rok military exercise was a " declaration of war . "
