( beijing time ) amid the debate over the us " nuclear posture assessment " regarding china as a target of nuclear attack , china 's official media yesterday praised its own strategic missile unit .
jiefangjun bao , renmin ribao , and other official newspapers all published " forging a peace shield for the republic " on their front pages and highly praised the troops of the second artillery corps , including the strategic missile and nuclear weapons units .
the article described this unit as using the " strategic missile training simulation system " to simulate nuclear attacks by an enemy country and a counterattack by the " red army " or china .
the " red army " rapidly drew up a combat plan by using modern procedures and deployed a new type of missile launching vehicle in the jungle of deep mountains and jungles .
this article , full of technical words , describes the application of new anti - jamming and anti - reconnaissance technologies by the second artillery corps to display its great prowess .
the article also said : missiles " took off from deep mountains to accurately hit targets . " they successfully carried out counter - attack operations .
