preventing koreans from " getting out of the embassy " china strengthens security of embassies and halls
( hong kong news ) the chinese police recently carried out an internal review of the intrusion of 25 koreans into the spanish embassy last week .
it is estimated that in beijing alone , more than 150 korean people are waiting for an opportunity to go to the rok . the authorities have strengthened security at the main embassies of the rok , japan , and western countries in the ambassador 's residence to prevent the recurrence of the incident .
sing tao jih pao reported yesterday that according to sources from the public security department , since 25 dprk people intruded into the west bank embassy on 14 march by surprise attacks , beijing police have further deployed its embassies in sensitive countries on the basis of enhancing security after the " 9.11 " incident . at the same time , they have also strengthened contact with personnel of the dprk and rok embassies in beijing .
according to sources , rok embassy staff told chinese officials that the rok side did not support the dprk people going to the rok in this way , and the rok does not want to see the recurrence of such incidents , so as to avoid having an impact on relations between china and the korean peninsula and the rok side promised to help china manage well its residents in beijing .
it has been disclosed that there are about 10,000 korean people living in the liangmahe river in the dongcheng and chaoyang districts in beijing , including korean people from north and south korea . they are mainly engaged in business in north korea 's style restaurants , bars , and other trades . because they are of the korean nationality , they are also on good terms with each other regardless of where they come from .
in the past , the korean authorities did not regard it as a key target for monitoring because there were not many people of the korean nationality in beijing , nor were they involved in many criminal cases like xinjiang people and heinan people .
according to the report , after the 14 march incident , the public security department first " asked " the doctor of germany , who was in charge of the 25 koreans , to " talk " with the public security department and immediately sent him to the airport to ask him to leave the country immediately .
subsequently , the public security and state security departments began to conduct internal reviews .
the review mainly covers two aspects : first , the security of the ambassador 's office area and second , the management of the personnel of the korean nationality in beijing .
in addition , the authorities have also asked relevant departments in jilin and other areas to take effective measures to prevent koreans from entering beijing illegally .
